ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T14:23:28.000Z","msg":"男人就得一碌9<br />\n但女人就幾十個lone<br />\n所以男人只可以搞到一個女人<br />\n但女人可以畀好多人同時搞"},{"pid":"f95e52f6c776d80e8d5ffad3a684adfc94260c7a","tid":562520,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T16:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/10/111245_64cf978e8d0f4882bf2a87e98ecfc9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F10%2F111245_64cf978e8d0f4882bf2a87e98ecfc9a4.png&h=81184940&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}